headline: Masco (MAS): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Masco has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small loss of 1.9% while holding steady at $64.06. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 10.1% gain during that period.
